sections.content:
標準入力に以下のようなJSONを送信:
```json
{
  "type": "call_tool",
  "params": {
    "name": "query",
    "arguments": {
      "sql": "SELECT * FROM users LIMIT 10"
    }
  }
}
```

標準出力例:
```json
{
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "[{\"id\":1,\"name\":\"Alice\"}]"
    }
  ],
  "isError": false
}
```
